def beautiful_indices(s, a, b, k)
    beautiful = []
    (0..s.length - a.length).each do |i|
        next unless s[i, a.length] == a
        (i - k..i + k).each do |j|
            next if j < 0 || j > s.length - b.length
            if s[j, b.length] == b
                beautiful << i
                break
            end
        end
    end
    beautiful.sort
end
